  "A rescue team uses a hydraulic tool called the 'Jaws of Life' to cut open a wrecked car. The small piston has an area of 2 cm^2, and the large piston has an area of 100 cm^2. If a firefighter pushes with 80 N of force, what force is produced at the cutting jaws?": "",
